CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 13, 1957, page B6, reads: "Supermarket Deluxe - The Loblaws' Bushton Avenue Supermarket has a large parking lot for customers seeking values in the refined atmosphere of the store. - All Photos by Teenie Harris"
TitMainTitle: View of Loblaw's Grocery Store at Brushton and Alsace Streets with sign in window "Grand Opening Thursday April 11th" and parking lot, Homewood-Brushton
